{"tid":897219,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭斯即將啟程訪問亞洲峰會演講將再批中國","createTime":"2018-11-10T16:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T00:52:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e692e726fdc0aedbdd3c8d4d979c91ec1f5ba2f0","tid":897219,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T16:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/158ADDBD-6DA7-4809-8670-70BDB61DBDB7_w1023_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F158ADDBD-6DA7-4809-8670-70BDB61DBDB7_w1023_r1_s.jpg&h=23d2aad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國副總統彭斯明天將啟程前往亞洲進行為期一個星期的訪問，並在11月17號出席亞太經合組織（APEC）峰會時就美國的&ldquo;印度-太平洋&rdquo;戰略發表重要演講。<br />\n<br />\n一名美國高級官員星期五就彭斯此次亞太之行的電話吹風會上透露，彭斯在巴布亞新幾內亞峰會上的這篇演講將&ldquo;深入和全面&rdquo;地闡述美國對地區安全構架以及戰略前景的構想。<br />\n<br />\n這名官員還說，預計彭斯在講話中對中國提出強烈批評，並宣布美國政府將出資600億美元，對印太地區各國提供經濟援助，以抗衡中國的&ldquo;一帶一路&rdquo;，加強美國在該地區的存在。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯副總統在上個月的一次長篇演講中對中國在政治、軍事和經濟等領域的一系列所作所為提出全面的尖銳批評，指出中國對外發放的高達數千億美元貸款使有的國家陷入無法償還債務陷阱，背上了&ldquo;巨債外交&rdquo;。對於美國的支援，美國高級官員星期五強調稱，美國的援助並非政府行為，而是民間型的，將為印太地區民眾帶去繁榮。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會上個月通過了一項被認為是與中國的一帶一路戰略直接抗衡的國際發展投資法案，該法案將海外私人投資公司與美國國際發展署的兩個部門合併，設立一個規模更大的美國國際發展金融公司，並為之提供600億美元資金，幫助全球貧困地區興建基礎設施和發展經濟。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯副總統在11日到18日長達8天的亞洲之行中將訪問日本、新加坡、澳大利亞和巴布亞新幾內亞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/Vice-President-Pence-Expected-In-Asia-To-Talk-Tough-On-China-20181110/4652826.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2FVice-President-Pence-Expected-In-Asia-To-Talk-Tough-On-China-20181110%2F4652826.html&d=KPZOplTh5I4OFh9HY0lUd1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=5141ffa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/Vice-President-Pence-Expected-In-Asia-To-Talk-Tough-On-China-20181110/4652826.html</a>"},{"pid":"d9b384a94274ea17421db03ec69a98b76932a2e9","tid":897219,"uid":97389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T17:28:16.000Z","msg":"亞洲版馬歇爾計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad5ac9a26e36d44f44adcef450074fc9d8e23da","tid":897219,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T23:44:25.000Z","msg":"印度，菲律賓，台灣，日本<br />\n<br />\n如果越南肯加入就正，不過無乜可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2a1aba61362e795574f0b85d97a79341f82340","tid":897219,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T23:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100ef54c205a1278c6180f6b2b48344e2b973241","tid":897219,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9b384a94274ea17421db03ec69a98b76932a2e9","tid":897219,"uid":97389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T17:28:16.000Z","msg":"亞洲版馬歇爾計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T23:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe71d99206423ff991ea4139e9b4542cce6f35e6","tid":897219,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b384a94274ea17421db03ec69a98b76932a2e9","tid":897219,"uid":97389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T17:28:16.000Z","msg":"亞洲版馬歇爾計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"想事半功倍<br />\n必須取消香港政策法配合"}]}